public class IteratorHelper
extends Object
implements javax.jcr.NodeIterator, javax.jcr.PropertyIterator, javax.jcr.nodetype.NodeTypeIterator, javax.jcr.StringIterator

IteratorHelper is a utility class which wraps an iterator and implements the various typed iterator interfaces.
